      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JASPER DARKE (2) has a strong record this track and trip with 14 wins and 15 placings from 37 starts. Missed the frame latest (30.15) when fourth over 515m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. LISA'S VOGUE (7) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 23.04 beating Stock's Gift. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Likely to be in the finish. KENZIES COMET (1) won by 2.25 lengths last start at this track 272m in a respectable 15.66. Bold showing expected again. FASCINATE GLORY (3) has claims again if she runs up to the latest effort.",
